reviewText: Didn't get to see these episodes when they were on air.  Loving it.
Got the whole set for my daughter. She loves them. Brings back great memories of her childhood, for both of us.
I always loved this show. It was done with opaque backgrounds as well as the characters. In my mind giving it unique look.
I purchased this for my son who loves it.
One of my grandson's all time favorites.
Loved this growing up and now can relive every episode in the comfort of my own room on my own time and no commercials :)
this is the final two seasons of the series this series is about a girl who can talk to animals. She uses her gift to help animals that she encounters.
Very happy with the quick shipping and good price.
